residential.headline: Spectacular Home
residential.description: This will please even the most discerning of buyers. Magnificent location up on Mt Panorama, overlooking the sleepy town of Bathurst. With 5 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms this will keep the family very cosy and even those who drop by. The stainless steel galley style kitchen will keep the chef cooking up a storm while the toys will be tinkered with out the back in the massive fully powered workshop. The entertaining area under the gabled roof includes a bar area and magnificent 12 seater spa, the tropical garden is impressive and reticulated by a bore.

residential.headline: RENOVATED DOUBLE BRICK BEAUTY
residential.description:
This home is all about the best of both worlds. The beauty of hard wearing, low maintenance double brick and the warm feeling of timber floors, big rooms and formal cornicing. Your new family friendly home is tasetfully renovated through out and it has the character and charm that you just have to share with your family and friends when you have your house warming. The kitchen is all about ease of use and functionality at meal times as it is also open plan with the dining room. There are 2 air conditioned lounge areas, as is the main and all bedrooms are built in and room enough for queen beds in all. In addition to the 3 bedrooms is the ideal office space, bright & airy with external windows. Car accomodation is provided by the double garage with workshop or third car space and it has great side access with no problems getting the boat or 4wd down the side. For your own inspection, call today as this is set to sell fast.
Available 7 days Dion Taylor 0448 197 835 or 4151 3233 dion@bundabergpropertygallery.com.au
Vast experience selling- Lifestyle Properties, Residential Properties, Land Sales, Project Management and extensive marketing knowledge to get you results.
